
		Wireless IMU 

(1) -	Start Wireless IMU application on the phone.
(2) -	Target IP Address = RPi's IP: click the VNC icon and you'll find it under Connectivity.
(3) -	Target IP Port = 5555
(4) -	Check the box "Run in background"

Run /Desktop/PythonPrograms/Accelerometer/wireless_imu.py to get output from Wireless IMU app

Decide servo movement according to the "y" value from:
Accelerometer	:     [x]    [(y)]    [z]
b'266741.15563, 3,  -1.411,  0.176,  9.722'
				=
			   4th value
			  separated with commas(,)